  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In the short adventure game <strong>The Supper</strong>, Ms. Appleton wakes up in her tavern's kitchen. The Voice inside her head is still there. It won't leave her alone. It commands her to serve a very special meal to some distinguished customers.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Octavi Navarro, creator of the critically acclaimed short games <i>Midnight Scenes, Unwelcome,</i> and <i>The Librarian</i>, comes a delicious treat for adventure game fans. A tiny snack to consume while you make your afternoon coffee or right before bed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore your surroundings:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171370/extras/c26af83a6900bc44db13331fadc1281a.avif?t=1774003640\" width=640 height=180 /></span><i>Find inspiration for your recipes in Ms. Appleton's kitchen or walking by the docks.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve many puzzles and cook:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171370/extras/cb16d82091bd1920e8e6d7b40b789fdc.avif?t=1774003640\" width=640 height=180 /></span><i>Help Ms. Appleton fetch all the ingredients for her delicious menu.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>...and don't forget to add a drop of \"Special Sauce\" before serving.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171370/extras/3d6e396cf6083211fe85896e0ba850eb.avif?t=1774003640\" width=640 height=180 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In the short adventure game <strong>The Supper</strong>, Ms. Appleton wakes up in her tavern's kitchen. The Voice inside her head is still there. It won't leave her alone. It commands her to serve a very special meal to some distinguished customers.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Octavi Navarro, creator of the critically acclaimed short games <i>Midnight Scenes, Unwelcome,</i> and <i>The Librarian</i>, comes a delicious treat for adventure game fans. A tiny snack to consume while you make your afternoon coffee or right before bed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore your surroundings:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171370/extras/c26af83a6900bc44db13331fadc1281a.avif?t=1774003640\" width=640 height=180 /></span><i>Find inspiration for your recipes in Ms. Appleton's kitchen or walking by the docks.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve many puzzles and cook:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171370/extras/cb16d82091bd1920e8e6d7b40b789fdc.avif?t=1774003640\" width=640 height=180 /></span><i>Help Ms. Appleton fetch all the ingredients for her delicious menu.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>...and don't forget to add a drop of \"Special Sauce\" before serving.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1171370/extras/3d6e396cf6083211fe85896e0ba850eb.avif?t=1774003640\" width=640 height=180 /></span></p>",
